Package com.google.api.client.googleapis.json

Documentation changed from old to new.

Added Classes
GoogleJsonRpcHttpTransport JSON-RPC 2.0 HTTP transport for RPC requests for Google API's, including both singleton and batched requests.
 

Changed Classes
AbstractJsonFeedParser Abstract base class for a Google JSON-C feed parser when the feed class is known in advance.
DiscoveryDocument Manages a JSON-formatted document from the experimental Google Discovery API version 0.1.
GoogleApi Manages HTTP requests for a version of a Google API service with a simple interface based on the new experimental Discovery API.
JsonCContent Serializes JSON-C content based on the data key/value mapping object for an item, wrapped in a {@code "data"} envelope.
JsonCParser Parses HTTP JSON-C response content into an data class of key/value pairs, assuming the data is wrapped in a {@code "data"} envelope.
JsonFeedParser Google JSON-C feed parser when the item class is known in advance.
JsonMultiKindFeedParser Google JSON-C feed parser when the item class can be computed from the kind.
